headline: General Electric (GE): Assessing Valuation as Shares Extend Recent Gains
summary: General Electric (GE) shares edged higher recently, building on gains from the past month. Investors are keeping an eye on the company's continued strong financial momentum, which has supported a steady upward trend in the stock. See our latest analysis for General Electric. GE’s momentum has been hard to ignore, with a year-to-date share price return of 85% and an impressive 5-year total shareholder return of nearly 570%.
